17 calendar quarter. For each cash device put into operation on a date
18 subsequent to a quarterly due date that has not been included in
19 computing the tax imposed and levied by the Mechanical Amusement Device
20 Tax Act, the tax shall be due and payable on the immediately succeeding
21 quarterly due date.
